verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Intro: D A G A (x2)
I want to see your face
I want to know your ways
Let your light shine upon us

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
I want to know your power
Come fill me once again
Lift me up in your hands of grace

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
And put a new song in my mouth
Of praise to you
And the world will see and fear
Your name (x2)
Worthy, worthy is the Lord (x3)
Most High
